# source-material/ — original design/export binaries, kept locally, deliberately
# not versioned. Untitled.fig is ~43MB, Dark Landing.png ~7MB, and the two .zips
# ~80MB combined; git history is permanent, so committing them would bloat every
# future clone. The design source of truth is the Claude Design project (see
# DECISIONS.md F2), and the exported .dc.html files in design-reference/ are
# versioned instead — those are what the CSS was ported from. Dark Landing.png is
# additionally a *stale* export and must not be treated as a reference.
# If these ever need versioning, use Git LFS rather than committing directly.
source-material/
